remarks: Swap antecedents.  If two conditions have a proposition as a consequence, their order is immaterial.  Third axiom of Frege's 1879 work but identical to ~ pm2.04 which can be proved from only ~ ax-mp , ~ ax-frege1 , and ~ ax-frege2 .  (Redundant) Axiom 8 of [Frege1879] p. 35.  (Contributed by RP, 24-Dec-2019.)  (New usage is discouraged.)
statement: ax-frege8 $p |- ( ( ph -> ( ps -> ch ) ) -> ( ps -> ( ph -> ch ) ) ) $.
